notes.noteText: This is the beginning of my case. Currently, everyone is a suspect. EVEN ME!

Previously incarcerated for extortion and let out of jail in 2015 (time frame of crimes?).
Arresting officer is Lilian Pfannerstill. Has a family member on the force, Lazaro Leuschke. I accused Hilario, and he was not the culprit.

Maggie has been in a poor mood since I have begun the case. She was intimately aware of the individuals that were targeted and why some were not targeted repeatedly. She drives a pickup truck and uses the word quickly.
Arrested for Grand Theft, and released shortly before the time of the crimes. Only alibi is cooking dinner.
